                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000402-24-off130 t18000402-24-cd131"></join>, two silver tea-spoons, value 3s. a glass decanter, value 1s. 6d. two glass salts, value 2s. a bason, value 6d. a towel, value 6d. two butter-boats, value 6d. and an ink-bottle, value 1d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
