             sworn. - I am the wife of Thomas Hodges; I keep the <placeName id="t18000402-24-crimeloc132">Burlington-arms, Old Burlington-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18000402-24-crimeloc132" type="placeName" value="Burlington-arms, Old Burlington-street"></interp>
