                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000402-24-off130 t18000402-24-crimeloc132"></join>: The latter end of January I missed three silver tea-spoons, a decanter, a bason, salts, and different articles; I suspected the prisoner; he was a <rs id="t18000402-24-deflabel133" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000402-24-defend227 t18000402-24-deflabel133"></join> in the house, to gather pots, and wash bottles; I know nothing of the robbery.</p>

